			description: [
				"&6&nDestruction Gadget&r"
				""
				"The primary tool for clearing out large areas quickly. It void-clears blocks instead of mining them, meaning the blocks will &cNOT&r drop as items. On the plus side, it completely ignores chests and other inventories to prevent accidental item loss, but you should still use it with caution."
			]
			id: "3D2C859382432B98"
			shape: "square"
			size: 1.0d
			subtitle: "&8[Click to read]"
