		{
			dependencies: ["5D1C5022E9C5A746"]
			description: [
				"&6&nCopy-Paste \\& Cut-Paste Gadgets&r"
				""
				"&b- Copy-Paste:&r Allows you to define a region by selecting two opposite corners, copy the layout, and paste it elsewhere. The tool checks your inventory and will only place the blocks if you have the required materials."
				""
				"&b- Cut-Paste:&r Functions like a clipboard move tool. It lifts an entire structure out of the world and pastes it into a new location, automatically clearing out the original spot."
			]
			id: "49833EE440E5EF63"
